                      ></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">
                    Fully Customizable
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  Arrange your meeting interface just the way you like it.
                  Control every aspect of your meeting experience.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      fill="currentColor"
                      class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600"
                    >
                      <path
                        d="M11.645 20.91l-.007-.003-.022-.012a15.247 15.247 0 01-.383-.218 25.18 25.18 0 01-4.244-3.17C4.688 15.36 2.25 12.174 2.25 8.25 2.25 5.322 4.714 3 7.688 3A5.5 5.5 0 0112 5.052 5.5 5.5 0 0116.313 3c2.973 0 5.437 2.322 5.437 5.25 0 3.925-2.438 7.111-4.739 9.256a25.175 25.175 0 01-4.244 3.17 15.247 15.247 0 01-.383.219l-.022.012-.007.004-.003.001a.752.752 0 01-.704 0l-.003-.001z"
                      ></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">
                    Ethical Technology
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  Choose a platform that aligns with your values. No ties to
                  organizations with unethical business practices.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

